@page "/"

<PageTitle>Wassel | COD Orders MVP</PageTitle>

<div class="landing-page">
	<section class="hero-panel">
		<div class="hero-copy">
			<p class="eyebrow">Algeria COD MVP</p>
			<h1>Capture, confirm, and ship orders from one clean workspace.</h1>
			<p class="hero-text">
				Start with the core product experience: a simple landing page, a fast login entry point,
				and a dashboard built around the confirmation workflow shown in your screenshot.
			</p>

			<div class="cta-row">
				<NavLink class="btn btn-primary btn-lg" href="/login">Open login</NavLink>
				<NavLink class="btn btn-secondary btn-lg" href="/dashboard">Preview dashboard</NavLink>
			</div>

			<div class="feature-pills" aria-label="Product highlights">
				<span>COD first</span>
				<span>French UI</span>
				<span>Dark dashboard</span>
				<span>Mobile-ready</span>
			</div>
		</div>

		<aside class="preview-card">
			<div class="preview-card__header">
				<div>
					<p class="eyebrow">MVP preview</p>
					<h2>Operations dashboard</h2>
				</div>
				<span class="mini-chip">Live view</span>
			</div>

			<div class="preview-stats">
				<div>
					<strong>128</strong>
					<span>orders today</span>
				</div>
				<div>
					<strong>87%</strong>
					<span>confirmed</span>
				</div>
				<div>
					<strong>58</strong>
					<span>wilayas</span>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="mini-board">
				<div class="mini-board__row">
					<span class="source-chip source-chip--shopify">Shopify</span>
					<span>Order #83041</span>
					<span class="status-chip status-chip--pending">En attente</span>
				</div>
				<div class="mini-board__row">
					<span class="source-chip source-chip--woo">WooCommerce</span>
					<span>Order #73460</span>
					<span class="status-chip status-chip--confirm">Confirmé</span>
				</div>
				<div class="mini-board__row">
					<span class="source-chip source-chip--manual">Manual</span>
					<span>Order #11209</span>
					<span class="status-chip status-chip--ship">Expédié</span>
				</div>
			</div>
		</aside>
	</section>

	<section class="mvp-grid">
		<article class="info-card">
			<p class="eyebrow">1. Landing page</p>
			<h3>Tell the story of the product</h3>
			<p>A concise product page that makes the workflow understandable before the first login.</p>
		</article>

		<article class="info-card">
			<p class="eyebrow">2. Login</p>
			<h3>Enter the workspace quickly</h3>
			<p>A minimal sign-in screen for agents and owners without setting up full authentication yet.</p>
		</article>

		<article class="info-card">
			<p class="eyebrow">3. Dashboard</p>
			<h3>Work like the screenshot</h3>
			<p>Search, filter, review orders, and update statuses in a dark confirmation dashboard.</p>
		</article>
	</section>
</div>
